name: string theories / carnival
description: String theory predicts that everything is made up of tiny strings resonating. Part of a series exploring the idea that we all are resonating connected strings. That everything is. A tribute to generative as a concept. Strings with different resonating modes generate space and time, and everything therein. A generative artwork by Marcelo Soria-Rodríguez, @msoriaro. Made with Processing, 960x540 looping mp4.
